               stealing, on the <rs id="t18261026-7-cd34" type="crimeDate">9th of October</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18261026-7-off33 t18261026-7-cd34"></join>, 1 handkerchief, value 2s., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18261026-7-victim134" type="victimName">
                        William 
                        Row
                     <interp inst="t18261026-7-victim134" type="surname" value="Row"></interp>
